00:00:00,040 --> 00:00:14,740
( Watch on Kissasia.vip )

1
00:01:00,100 --> 00:01:02,900
=Daughter of Fortune=

2
00:01:02,900 --> 00:01:05,460
(Adapted from the novel
"Phoenix Palace Dream" by Lan Jiujiu)

3
00:01:05,540 --> 00:01:08,460
=Episode 3=

4
00:01:11,040 --> 00:01:12,480
That's a brutal beating.

5
00:01:14,240 --> 00:01:15,760
This is far too heavy.

6
00:01:15,760 --> 00:01:16,880
She won't be able to walk after this.

7
00:01:16,880 --> 00:01:18,200
Look at all this blood.

8
00:01:18,600 --> 00:01:20,080
Will she be beaten to death?

9
00:01:22,320 --> 00:01:23,520
I doubt she'll even survive.

10
00:01:23,800 --> 00:01:24,760
How pitiful.

11
00:01:24,840 --> 00:01:26,880
We must never offend
the Lady of Bright Deportment.

12
00:01:29,040 --> 00:01:31,120
Pay attention, Ladies.

13
00:01:31,480 --> 00:01:32,960
Whether you become a Noble Lady

14
00:01:33,320 --> 00:01:34,800
or a useless cripple

15
00:01:35,640 --> 00:01:37,680
depends entirely on your own choices.

16
00:01:38,520 --> 00:01:39,840
Cut out her tongue.

17
00:02:12,040 --> 00:02:14,520
Are you here to watch
your owner's punishment?

18
00:02:15,040 --> 00:02:16,240
Shen Zhinian is terrified.

19
00:02:16,400 --> 00:02:18,290
She surely won't go
to the Cold Palace tonight.

20
00:02:18,920 --> 00:02:20,360
She will certainly go.

21
00:02:23,880 --> 00:02:26,700
Dowager Consort Liu always thought
Your Ladyship wasn't ruthless enough.

22
00:02:26,720 --> 00:02:28,240
She's making a point to Your Ladyship.

23
00:02:28,560 --> 00:02:30,240
The palace rules dictate flogging.

24
00:02:30,320 --> 00:02:31,640
But she's using illegal torture.

25
00:02:32,360 --> 00:02:34,040
I'm going to take
the palace rules to her

26
00:02:34,040 --> 00:02:35,520
and read them to her one by one.

27
00:02:35,600 --> 00:02:36,990
Please don't be angry, Your Ladyship.

28
00:02:37,440 --> 00:02:38,560
She is a Dowager Consort

29
00:02:38,800 --> 00:02:40,400
and the Emperor's nominal foster mother.

30
00:02:40,640 --> 00:02:41,880
Even His Majesty defers to her.

31
00:02:44,840 --> 00:02:46,640
Your Ladyship,
I've investigated everything.

32
00:02:46,700 --> 00:02:48,630
Someone planted forbidden
flowers in the Cold Palace.

33
00:02:48,640 --> 00:02:49,600
A large patch

34
00:02:49,680 --> 00:02:51,120
has bloomed in the palace.

35
00:02:51,320 --> 00:02:52,480
Clear them out now.

36
00:02:52,640 --> 00:02:53,080
Yes.

37
00:02:53,440 --> 00:02:54,000
Wait.

38
00:02:55,320 --> 00:02:56,400
Use the flowers as bait.

39
00:02:56,920 --> 00:02:58,440
Let's see who actually planted them.

40
00:02:59,320 --> 00:03:00,080
Have men watch it.

41
00:03:00,640 --> 00:03:02,600
If anyone dares to go to
the Cold Palace tonight,

42
00:03:02,920 --> 00:03:04,200
report back at once.

43
00:03:04,440 --> 00:03:05,280
Yes.

44
00:03:05,420 --> 00:03:08,500
(Cold Palace)

45
00:03:11,820 --> 00:03:12,920
It's already the hour of Zi.

46
00:03:13,500 --> 00:03:14,600
Your Majesty guessed wrong.

47
00:03:14,960 --> 00:03:16,080
She won't be coming tonight.

48
00:03:23,800 --> 00:03:25,320
She actually dared to come.

49
00:03:25,760 --> 00:03:27,040
She has some courage

50
00:03:27,200 --> 00:03:28,360
for taking such a risk.

51
00:03:29,120 --> 00:03:30,680
But she doesn't seem to be coming over.

52
00:03:31,320 --> 00:03:33,280
She's heading toward
where Xu Baoqin is held.

53
00:03:35,680 --> 00:03:36,640
You go back first.

54
00:03:38,360 --> 00:03:39,240
Yes.

55
00:03:47,440 --> 00:03:48,200
Don't be afraid.

56
00:03:48,640 --> 00:03:49,920
I'm here to bring you medicine.

57
00:03:50,840 --> 00:03:51,800
I mean no harm.

58
00:04:06,280 --> 00:04:07,600
I will bribe the guards here.

59
00:04:08,480 --> 00:04:09,720
I won't let you go hungry.

60
00:04:11,760 --> 00:04:13,640
It's so dark in the Cold Palace.

61
00:04:14,640 --> 00:04:16,520
I'll leave this lantern for you.

62
00:04:17,000 --> 00:04:18,000
There's nothing more

63
00:04:18,360 --> 00:04:19,480
I can do.

64
00:04:24,320 --> 00:04:25,120
Take care.

65
00:04:41,240 --> 00:04:42,480
She framed you like that.

66
00:04:43,000 --> 00:04:44,400
Why do you still want to save her?

67
00:04:44,800 --> 00:04:45,880
She was wrong.

68
00:04:46,200 --> 00:04:47,500
But to suffer such cruel torture

69
00:04:47,760 --> 00:04:48,840
is simply too much.

70
00:04:51,000 --> 00:04:51,960
In this palace,

71
00:04:52,280 --> 00:04:53,920
there is no room for your kind heart.

72
00:04:54,640 --> 00:04:55,880
I'm no saint.

73
00:04:56,400 --> 00:04:57,600
I'm just an ordinary person.

74
00:04:58,200 --> 00:04:59,480
I can be soft-hearted,

75
00:05:00,060 --> 00:05:01,320
but I also know how to survive.

76
00:05:02,200 --> 00:05:02,920
Your Ladyship,

77
00:05:03,040 --> 00:05:05,240
I saw someone enter
the Cold Palace with my own eyes.

78
00:05:05,240 --> 00:05:06,440
They are inside right now.

79
00:05:06,440 --> 00:05:07,680
It's over. Quick, hide.

80
00:05:08,400 --> 00:05:11,000
I'd like to see
who is desecrating the palace grounds.

81
00:05:11,480 --> 00:05:12,640
Follow me in and seize them.

82
00:05:20,160 --> 00:05:21,640
(That's strange.)

83
00:05:22,120 --> 00:05:23,320
(Ever since I was poisoned,)

84
00:05:23,680 --> 00:05:24,600
(my internal organs)

85
00:05:24,600 --> 00:05:26,290
(have felt like they
were on fire every day.)

86
00:05:26,800 --> 00:05:27,880
(But holding her hand)

87
00:05:28,880 --> 00:05:30,760
(actually makes me
feel quite comfortable.)

88
00:05:32,600 --> 00:05:34,080
(Let's test her one more time.)

89
00:05:35,500 --> 00:05:37,320
Didn't you want to
learn the art of seduction?

90
00:05:42,720 --> 00:05:43,880
I wonder

91
00:05:48,880 --> 00:05:50,600
where you would like to begin.

92
00:05:51,720 --> 00:05:52,640
(What is he up to?)

93
00:05:53,000 --> 00:05:53,560
(Never mind.)

94
00:05:53,570 --> 00:05:54,580
(I'll just go along with it.)

95
00:05:55,600 --> 00:05:58,120
If I'm to learn,
I want to learn something different.

96
00:06:00,720 --> 00:06:01,760
I'll be on top,

97
00:06:02,520 --> 00:06:03,560
and he'll be on the bottom.

98
00:06:08,100 --> 00:06:10,100
♪You do not know♪

99
00:06:10,260 --> 00:06:13,820
♪The partridge's cry
is full of resentment♪

100
00:06:14,600 --> 00:06:16,520
Senior Attendant Shen,
you are quite bold.

101
00:06:17,440 --> 00:06:19,280
Attendant Li, you said it yourself.

102
00:06:19,680 --> 00:06:20,880
If I want to be seductive,

103
00:06:21,040 --> 00:06:22,420
I can't afford to be timid.

104
00:06:22,420 --> 00:06:27,460
♪Broken dreams,
listening to the light rain♪

105
00:06:27,860 --> 00:06:31,540
♪Bitter cold, bringing mist to the eyes♪

106
00:06:31,560 --> 00:06:33,440
Attendant Li, teach me well.

107
00:06:33,880 --> 00:06:35,160
If you do a good job,

108
00:06:35,800 --> 00:06:37,000
you'll be richly rewarded.

109
00:06:37,140 --> 00:06:40,700
♪Flowers bloom and fall in shame♪

110
00:06:40,740 --> 00:06:47,220
♪If we meet again,
the peaches will be warm♪

111
00:06:47,540 --> 00:06:54,180
♪Spring breeze passes,
dancing through the years♪

112
00:06:57,240 --> 00:06:59,240
You clearly know
the ways of men and women.

113
00:07:00,560 --> 00:07:02,080
Why do you still need me to teach you?

114
00:07:02,480 --> 00:07:04,400
Attendant Li, don't you know

115
00:07:04,960 --> 00:07:06,360
that if one serves with beauty,

116
00:07:07,000 --> 00:07:08,320
as beauty fades,

117
00:07:08,680 --> 00:07:09,840
love withers,

118
00:07:10,280 --> 00:07:11,360
and when love withers,

119
00:07:11,600 --> 00:07:12,880
favor ends?

120
00:07:14,320 --> 00:07:15,200
What I want

121
00:07:15,800 --> 00:07:17,380
is for the moon to shine only on me.

122
00:07:17,380 --> 00:07:21,260
♪Spring breeze passes,
composing the fleeting years♪

123
00:07:23,480 --> 00:07:25,440
Emperors have been fickle
since ancient times.

124
00:07:25,920 --> 00:07:27,280
I'm afraid you'll be disappointed.

125
00:07:28,120 --> 00:07:29,960
Then, I'll just have
to settle for his body.

126
00:07:30,720 --> 00:07:32,600
If I can hold the moon
in my arms every night,

127
00:07:32,620 --> 00:07:33,560
that would be nice too.

128
00:07:34,120 --> 00:07:35,680
You have grand ambitions, huh?

129
00:07:38,200 --> 00:07:39,480
A small token of appreciation.

130
00:07:39,800 --> 00:07:40,840
(Ten Taels of Silver)
Please accept this, Attendant.

131
00:07:46,120 --> 00:07:47,040
Ten taels?

132
00:07:47,760 --> 00:07:49,560
You want to control a man's heart

133
00:07:50,280 --> 00:07:51,560
for only ten taels?

134
00:07:54,640 --> 00:07:56,320
A heart that doesn't shine solely on me

135
00:07:56,760 --> 00:07:57,560
isn't worth much.

136
00:08:00,480 --> 00:08:01,800
"Isn't worth much," huh?

137
00:08:03,200 --> 00:08:04,040
Fine.

138
00:08:05,040 --> 00:08:06,640
I will teach you right now.

139
00:08:11,960 --> 00:08:13,360
Why did you bring me here?

140
00:08:13,960 --> 00:08:14,720
To know your enemy

141
00:08:15,080 --> 00:08:16,480
is to be victorious in every battle.

142
00:08:17,580 --> 00:08:18,480
First, learn to drink.

143
00:08:18,920 --> 00:08:19,800
Drink?

144
00:08:20,240 --> 00:08:21,040
Black Zhen Liquor.

145
00:08:21,680 --> 00:08:22,800
It goes down like fire,

146
00:08:23,040 --> 00:08:24,280
burning the heart and soul.

147
00:08:25,320 --> 00:08:26,400
It is his favorite.

148
00:08:30,600 --> 00:08:32,160
Half qian of Nine-Steamed Spring,

149
00:08:32,560 --> 00:08:34,120
one qian of Amber Settle.

150
00:08:34,720 --> 00:08:35,920
Gaze at Thousand-Mountain Moon,

151
00:08:36,600 --> 00:08:38,080
and have the winter snow once more.

152
00:08:39,040 --> 00:08:39,880
Finally,

153
00:08:40,240 --> 00:08:41,760
add a little Zhen poison.

154
00:08:43,720 --> 00:08:44,800
Zhen poison?

155
00:08:45,000 --> 00:08:46,280
Won't I die if I drink it?

156
00:08:46,500 --> 00:08:47,600
You must control the amount.

157
00:08:48,160 --> 00:08:51,400
With the right amount, you'll feel like
you're floating to heaven.

158
00:08:51,770 --> 00:08:52,680
But if it's too much...

159
00:08:53,160 --> 00:08:54,280
I'll die on the spot.

160
00:08:56,520 --> 00:08:57,160
Have a taste.

161
00:08:59,360 --> 00:09:01,080
(It can't be real Zhen poison.)

162
00:09:01,360 --> 00:09:02,800
(One drop of Zhen poison is lethal.)

163
00:09:03,200 --> 00:09:04,520
(If he wanted to kill me,)

164
00:09:04,530 --> 00:09:06,240
(he wouldn't go
through all this trouble.)

165
00:09:12,000 --> 00:09:13,640
If I were serving liquor to His Majesty,

166
00:09:14,120 --> 00:09:15,440
should I feed him like this?

167
00:09:18,200 --> 00:09:19,320
He won't drink it.

168
00:09:19,920 --> 00:09:20,720
Oh.

169
00:09:22,920 --> 00:09:23,720
What about this?

170
00:09:58,640 --> 00:09:59,400
Your Ladyship,

171
00:09:59,720 --> 00:10:01,240
someone broke into the liquor cellar.

172
00:10:01,600 --> 00:10:02,760
Hurry up and catch them.

173
00:10:03,190 --> 00:10:03,960
Yes, Your Ladyship.

174
00:10:04,840 --> 00:10:05,240
Let's go

175
00:10:05,520 --> 00:10:06,000
take a look.

176
00:10:07,980 --> 00:10:13,500
(Bamboo Dew Spring)

177
00:10:13,520 --> 00:10:14,200
Tell me,

178
00:10:14,880 --> 00:10:15,760
who are you?

179
00:10:16,290 --> 00:10:17,560
Why did you come to the palace?

180
00:10:19,160 --> 00:10:20,760
My name is Shen Zhinian.

181
00:10:22,160 --> 00:10:23,600
I entered the palace

182
00:10:24,640 --> 00:10:27,160
to marry the most powerful man

183
00:10:28,080 --> 00:10:30,200
and attain the highest power.

184
00:10:31,600 --> 00:10:33,000
So, it's power you're after.

185
00:10:36,200 --> 00:10:37,400
It's not power.

186
00:10:37,920 --> 00:10:39,080
It's safety.

187
00:10:39,960 --> 00:10:42,120
It's to live a good life.

188
00:10:42,330 --> 00:10:46,710
♪Faint rouge hides
the tenderness in the eyes♪

189
00:10:46,750 --> 00:10:49,860
♪Every step is treacherous,
regardless of the world♪

190
00:10:51,760 --> 00:10:53,520
Then, do you know who I am?

191
00:10:54,040 --> 00:10:55,520
Yes.

192
00:10:57,580 --> 00:11:00,460
♪In the palace, through dawn and dusk,
who keeps a lamp burning♪

193
00:11:00,640 --> 00:11:02,720
Nangong Xuanyu.

194
00:11:14,780 --> 00:11:19,900
♪Broken dreams,
listening to the light rain♪

195
00:11:21,620 --> 00:11:26,860
♪Bitter cold, bringing mist to the eyes♪

196
00:11:28,500 --> 00:11:30,860
♪If we don't meet♪

197
00:11:31,060 --> 00:11:34,300
♪Flowers bloom and fall in shame♪

198
00:11:34,500 --> 00:11:41,020
♪If we meet again,
the peaches will be warm♪

199
00:11:41,380 --> 00:11:47,820
♪Spring breeze passes,
dancing through the years♪

200
00:11:48,180 --> 00:11:54,500
♪Brewing longing,
remembering past lives♪

201
00:11:55,020 --> 00:12:01,700
♪Hard to meet, and just as hard to part♪

202
00:12:01,700 --> 00:12:08,580
♪Who planted the beans
that grew into lotuses?♪

203
00:12:08,820 --> 00:12:14,700
♪Spring breeze passes,
composing the fleeting years♪

204
00:12:15,620 --> 00:12:22,220
♪Clouds on Mount Wu,
no sails on the sea♪

205
00:12:22,380 --> 00:12:29,060
♪Wanting to fold
my heart into a paper kite♪

206
00:12:29,340 --> 00:12:35,780
♪But the ties are too tangled to sever♪

